{
  "name": "LineFormat",
  "summary": "<p>对于线条，<strong>LineFormat</strong>对象包含该线条自身的格式信息；对于有边界的形状，该对象包含形状的边界的格式信息。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Line</strong>属性可返回一个 <strong>LineFormat</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给第一张工作表添加一条蓝色虚线。在该线的起点有一个短而窄的椭圆，在该线的终点有一个长而宽的三角形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> = msoLineDashDotDot\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">128</span>)\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadShort\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadOval\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadNarrow\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadLong\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadTriangle\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadWide\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状线条的样式是否为双细线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Style</span> == msoLineThinThin)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表线条和箭头格式。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code>*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "BackColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>ColorFormat</strong>对象，它代表指定的填充背景色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个形状线条的背景色设置为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状线条的背景色是否为绿色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ColorFormat",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "BeginArrowheadLength",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定线条起点的箭头的长度。<strong>MsoArrowheadLength</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表中添加直线。该直线的起点是一个短而窄的椭圆，而该直线的终点则是一个长而宽的三角形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadShort\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadOval\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadNarrow\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadLong\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadTriangle\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadWide\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状线条始端的箭头长度是否为长型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> == msoArrowheadLong)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoArrowheadLength",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "BeginArrowheadStyle",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定线条起点的箭头样式。<strong>MsoArrowheadStyle</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表中添加直线。该直线的起点是一个短而窄的椭圆，而该直线的终点则是一个长而宽的三角形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadShort\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadOval\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadNarrow\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadLong\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadTriangle\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadWide\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状线条始端的箭头样式是否为菱形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> == msoArrowheadDiamond)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoArrowheadStyle",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "BeginArrowheadWidth",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定线条起点的箭头宽度。<strong>MsoArrowheadWidth</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表中添加直线。该直线的起点是一个短而窄的椭圆，而该直线的终点则是一个长而宽的三角形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadShort\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadOval\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadNarrow\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadLong\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadTriangle\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadWide\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状线条起点的箭头宽度是否为宽。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> == msoArrowheadWide)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoArrowheadWidth",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DashStyle",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定直线的虚线样式。可以是 <strong>MsoLineDashStyle</strong> 常量之一。可读/写 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表中添加蓝色的虚线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> = msoLineDashDotDot\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">128</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向活动工作表添加一条红色实线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">27</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">230</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> = msoLineSolid\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoLineDashStyle",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "EndArrowheadLength",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoArrowheadLength</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoArrowheadLength</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadLengthMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadShort</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadLengthMedium</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadLong</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定线条末尾的箭头的长度。<strong>MsoArrowheadLength</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表中添加直线。该直线的起点是一个短而窄的椭圆，而该直线的终点则是一个长而宽的三角形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddLine</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadShort\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadOval\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BeginArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadNarrow\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> = msoArrowheadLong\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadStyle</span> = msoArrowheadTriangle\n    line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadWidth</span> = msoArrowheadWide\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状线条终点的箭头长度是否为短型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> line = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(line.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EndArrowheadLength</span> == msoArrowheadShort)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoArrowheadLength",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "EndArrowheadStyle",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoArrowheadStyle</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoArrowheadStyle</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadNone</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadOval</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadStyleMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadDiamond</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadOpen</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadStealth</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoArrowheadTriangle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定线条端点的箭头样式。<strong>MsoArrowheadStyle</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
